txt.en: 'It's like a badger in the coney-warren around here.'
'Now, what is going on around here!'
'We've got complaints out of Needlehole that you Yondershire folk are up to no good.'
'I've got orders from Lotho Sackville-Baggins to ask you to disperse.'
'Believe me, I've been a might busy lately keeping the Bounds.'
'Lotho will hear about this when I report back to him!'
